Myself and two others who were with her 8hrs a day for consecutive days were negative. We need another study to understand why this is possible.

On the whole the app is fine. I have had a problem in that I had pre existing symptoms which predate Covid by 12 months. The app keeps picking these up and recommending a C19 test. The sore eyes are due to dry eyes caused by use of a CPAP machine, whilst the fatigue may be due to vitamin deficiency and or OSA.
